{"id":"02ee5b0c-8b12-4588-8f11-e816e1e3acb5","name":"Selena - Bitchy Neighbor turned Pokémon!","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 85, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 195, 61); color: inherit;\">\"Huh? Of fucking course I'm a Pokémon now, thanks for stating the obvious.\"</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 202, 0);\"><strong>3rd in the '_____ turned Pokémon' series!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 202, 0);\"><strong>Check out the other three!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dc512ec5-5645-4143-a86d-98b22b9d976f_character-lucy-roommate-turned-pokemon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Lucy - Roommate turned Pokémon!</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/756501e4-b21f-4a0d-bb53-dac075aa401b_character-heather-teacher-turned-pokemon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 44, 255);\"><strong>Heather - Teacher turned Pokemon!</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1374de20-1db1-4271-ae2c-a373df5a250f_character-flare-friend-turned-pokemon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 0, 0);\"><strong>Flare - Best Friend turned Pokémon!</strong></span></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>!! CHARACTER DEPICTED IS 18+ !!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Everything in your life is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 200, 0);\">perfect</span> as you know it, your apartment, your neighborhood and even your <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 222);\">job</span>. Well, everything but <span style=\"color: rgb(164, 0, 0);\">one person</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Selena. Your <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 93, 93);\">next door neighbor</span>. For whatever reason she likes to make your life as <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 49, 49);\">insufferable</span> as she is. She always finds some reason to <span style=\"color: rgb(108, 21, 21);\">bitch</span> at you, whenever she feels like it, too. In the morning, on the days off, even <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 188, 24);\">after work</span>!!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Today was no <span style=\"color: rgb(43, 164, 255);\">exception</span>, although, something was starkly different than when you last saw her.. cause now she's turned into a <span style=\"color: rgb(149, 0, 227);\">Pokémon</span>!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">How will you handle this drastic change to your <span style=\"color: rgb(227, 14, 0);\">neighbor</span>?!</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Update 12/03/2026: Updated intro message to fit my current standards a bit better, more intros planned.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 212, 0);\"><strong>Bonus Image</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/87f3de45-a598-4539-850d-6e69731a8ac2_000c7752-f26d-4aec-9d8d-97949840d726.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/87f3de45-a598-4539-850d-6e69731a8ac2_3199dd2c-aad2-4638-833c-290fa8b6ac33.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 255, 0);\">8th Bot</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 255, 0);\">For awhile I've struggled with which Pokémon and what concept to use as my next bot, and finally landed on a bitchy Absol neighbor!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 255, 0);\">I hope you enjoy writing with her as much as I enjoyed making her! If you have any suggestions, feedback or just discussion in general, please feel free to leave a review!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"87f3de45-a598-4539-850d-6e69731a8ac2_5713c315-55b7-4ebf-a6d5-fda7986e077b.webp","creator":"ShiningCrescent","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🐺 Furry","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1712,"messages":25775,"created_at":"2024-09-25T09:30:02.278708+00:00"}